{"tid":680922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港「六四遊行」人數較去年上升160人","createTime":"2018-05-27T14:38:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T09:45:00.000Z","uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bd8341fd2908151587f60fb1bc322d4739ad1400","tid":680922,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T14:38:59.000Z","msg":"<strong>警方: 2017年六四遊行人數只有450人</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-40149244\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-40149244&d=FFCZ1dYqrAUht%2BKZNxHPP4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=47a8bd93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-40149244&h=cceab898\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-40149244</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>警方現表示2018年六四遊行人數有610人.  </strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1398446-20180527.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1398446-20180527.htm&d=FFCZ1dYqrAUht%2BKZNxHPP4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=989b78dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1398446-20180527.htm&h=8a5a2ed2\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1398446-20180527.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n支聯會稱1100人參加六四遊行　警方：高峰610人<br />\n2018-05-27 HKT 18:13<br />\n<br />\n支聯會發起遊行，悼念六四事件29周年，大會表示有1100人參加，警方說，遊行最高峰有610人參與。<br />\n<br />\n遊行隊伍下午5時許抵達終點中聯辦，參加者將「結束一黨專政」的貼紙及宣言貼在中聯辦外，遊行之後結束。<br />\n<br />\n支聯會主席何俊仁對遊行人數表示難得及欣慰，他說在炎熱天氣下，仍然有很多人參與，不受恐嚇及威脅，表達堅定平反六四的心願，希望六四集會一如以往有大批市民出席。"},{"pid":"120a5637f6390a09cfd22c7fd28bb1e9db9c1266","tid":680922,"uid":4525,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T14:53:54.000Z","msg":"勁過港獨"},{"pid":"fac5d131612c388448fd148854afce4866fc607e","tid":680922,"uid":20898,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2